# Inversion of Control (IoC) 🔄

## 📖 What is Inversion of Control (IoC)?

**Inversion of Control (IoC)** is a design principle where the control of object creation and dependency management is transferred from the programmer to the Spring Framework.

In simple words:

> **Instead of creating objects yourself, Spring creates and manages them for you.**

IoC is one of the core concepts of the Spring Framework.

---

# 🎯 Why IoC?

Without IoC:

❌ Manual Object Creation

❌ Tight Coupling

❌ Difficult Maintenance

❌ Difficult Unit Testing

With IoC:

✅ Automatic Object Creation

✅ Loose Coupling

✅ Easy Testing

✅ Better Code Reusability

---

