# 🏗 Without IoC

```java id="wjlwm3"
class Engine {

}

class Car {

    private Engine engine =
            new Engine();

}
```

Problems:

* Tight Coupling
* Hard to Replace Engine
* Difficult Testing

---

# 🏗 With IoC

```java id="wjlwm4"
@Component
class Engine {

}

@Component
class Car {

    private Engine engine;

    public Car(Engine engine) {
        this.engine = engine;
    }

}
```

Spring automatically creates and injects the Engine object.

